name: Devi gathered floral-print mini dress
description: The romantic spirit of this 'Devi' dress is a signature of Zimmermann. It's made from silk-chiffon that's gathered across the yoke, sleeves and waistline to flow effortlessly. Complement the peachy pinks with a matching lip.
